{"tid":23230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[單親媽溺斃]痛失好媽媽 19歲女崩潰：好後悔冇盡囡嘅責任","createTime":"2016-12-04T21:31:45.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-05T02:23:22.000Z","uid":26190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"16c36b0d346c430e67869bf4409309d7492eff91","tid":23230,"uid":26190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T21:31:45.000Z","msg":"「佢臨返工前都會游水，但今日出咗去就冇返過嚟！」42歲姓林女子上午於屯門蝴蝶灣泳灘溺斃，遺下現正就讀副學士課程的19歲姓馮獨女，陰陽相隔，女兒接受《蘋果》訪問時崩潰痛哭：「好掛住佢...」。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，死者的丈夫6年前因糖尿病併發逝世，自始母兼父職，任機場保安員養家，獨力養大女兒。死者熱愛游泳，每日返工前必會到海灘游早水，惟今晨卻不幸遇溺，一去不返。愛女痛失雙親，孤苦無依，就連母親的殮葬費亦成問題，她回憶起母親多年來克勤克儉，為她供書教學，不禁自責：「佢好錫我，好想帶佢食好嘢，好後悔冇盡囡嘅責任！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20150717/53985378\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20150717%2F53985378&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mUsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=1556a6c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20150717%2F53985378&h=a978f01c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20150717/53985378</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f29d01ccde4f48dfc6aaa9fdf5b90f865c40c909","tid":23230,"uid":11156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T21:40:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6acce78b4de0aee7f70cbd3cbf834744ea51e83c","tid":23230,"uid":45232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T21:43:43.000Z","msg":"20150717"},{"pid":"3bacf5fc07177788cffe99f1166cd9c90ffc2e66","tid":23230,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T21:44:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f62c857d4549320b254c6ba4b58d56b67bd7188","tid":23230,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply